Package author: Andy Salnikov

Brief description:
==================

This package contains a bunch of psana input modules which are used by
multi-process psana:

XtcMPMasterInput
	input module for master process, reads the data from XTC files 
	and sends datagrams to clients
	
ShmemMPMasterInput
	input module for master process, reads XTC data from shared memory
	and sends datagrams to clients

XtcMPWorkerInput
	input module for worker processes, receives data sent by the two 
	above modules
	